-------------------------
Fix "make check" failures
-------------------------
On my fork, I can get nvc.exe but "make check" fails.

Symptoms of "make check" faiulres look not deterministic.
Maybe, this problem is caused by fsckin' resident anti-virus software?
I've tried to disable my anti-virus software, but no joy.
I use AVG Internet Security 2012 at this moment.

See more detail:

 $ git clone git@github.com:hiyuh/nvc.git
 $ cd ~/git-repos/nvc

